Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:03.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the powers of the Soul Reaper\Nwere thrust upon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my whole world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Substitute Soul Reaper,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:11.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wield this sword\Nwith all of my soul and strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:14.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to protect my precious friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:25.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:30.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one can take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:36.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never fade, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:49.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun never blinds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:54.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a flower that blooms in shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:01:04.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exhale those feelings you hold inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:14.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only;\Nnow and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:24.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The day may come\Nwhen all will rise against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:30.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:34.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never give up, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:40.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,TIME NOTICE THAT\NYOU SHOULD NOTICE THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:44.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,NOTICE THAT THERE’S NO OTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Lirin.\NPleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:04.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a game, a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:27.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:29.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:38.50,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara's Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Wait a second! Hey!\N– Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you do that all\Nof a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could I leave my body\Nwith you for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:04.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s all right.\NBut what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad was kidnapped too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:10.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is attacking us\None by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:14.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to leave\Nmy body laying around unoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:15.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:16.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:19.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?! So you're finally acknowledging\Nmy abilities, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me earlier\Nif that's the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:24.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:27.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take responsibility for your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:31.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What’s with those guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:32.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was incredibly hard\Nto fight them--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:36.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It means that there's more to fighting\Nthan charging at your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:40.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Aizen is involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara, did you find out anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:48.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I analyzed\Nthe telephone conversation…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but there wasn't a Riemon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which is the spirit equivalent\Nof a voiceprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:52.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, it probably means
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that they're not humans\Nor Soul Reapers…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:02.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiritual Pressure of those\Nthree are definitely a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:07.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your ability to sense Spiritual Pressure\Nis as poor as always…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:08.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:13.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If the enemies' powers\Nare derived from Kido,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:17.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it will be difficult to directly\Nattack them with zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:18.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So does that mean
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:21.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that I can't damage them\Nwith Zangetsu's Getsugatensho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In theory, yes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:27.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, can you control\Nthe power of that technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:32.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It has enough power to match\NCaptain Kuchiki's Senbonzakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we do defeat the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:34.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we'll suffer too much\Ncollateral damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:37.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you use Bankai,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you can do Kido-type attacks,\Ncan't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:43.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not confident that I can\Ncontrol my Zabimaru in Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those in the ranks of lieutenant\Nand higher, like me…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,are allowed only limited powers\Nwhile in the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:50.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, you're the only one\Nwe can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hit them with your\NQuincy's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't have to\Ntell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:01.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy targeted\NMiss Inoue and Master Sado first
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:04.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,because they were easier\Nto take out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:07.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going exactly\Nas they planned…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:18.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patronage.\NThis is Urahara's Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:33.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue our game\Nat the Karakura Museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:34.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to\NChad and Inoue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:38.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are they safe--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:39.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they're\Nat the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Again--?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Put your minds at ease\Nand follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:03.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we don't know where this enemy\Nis going to come from,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watch behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:10.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But did you have to modify me\Ninto a backpack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull. That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind if\Nit was Inoue's back,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but why do I have to be\Non this guy's back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I knew\NI was going to carry you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:23.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have modified you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji and I have become\NSoul Reapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so people can't see us--!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:32.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would have preferred\NInoue's back…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida… If something happens,\Nyou can throw him away and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:42.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have important tools\Ninside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wha--…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I took out some of the stuffing\Nin your stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:07:00.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and modified you\Nso I can stuff things in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:02.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… Nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:04.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think he'd sell if\Nyou made lots of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sue you for infringement\Nof stuffed animal rights!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:23.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, should someone\Nkeep watch outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, they have hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:45.23,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Special Exhibit for Ichigo Kurosaki\Nand the Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've accepted your invitation!\NCome out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hide and go seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:58.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:03.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you find us,\Nwe'll return your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:07.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:10.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Also, leave your weapons here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:15.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know\Nwhat'll happen to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Threatening us, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Put them in that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.37,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zabi- “maru” (“circle”)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They’re screwing with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think a circle is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.91,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zan-“ketsu” (“butt”)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pummel them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You two, don't fall for\Ntheir cheap shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Shut up!\N– Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:39.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:41.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's going\Njust the way she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:54.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:58.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Not really…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been feeling\Nstrange Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,since we've been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:04.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:08.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon, tell me if anything out of\Nthe ordinary happens behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the same room\Ngoes on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was this building ever this big?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're over here…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over here… Over here…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over here… Over here…\NOver here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:37.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The way to get out of\Na labyrinth is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to advance with your hand\Nagainst the same wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't appear to\Nbe anything especially strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:57.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We kept going right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So this room should be\Nthe room next to the hall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:00.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,from where we entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:03.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But instead there's another entrance\Nto the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same room…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:15.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon! I told you to keep watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:24.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:27.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but there wasn't anything\Nout of the ordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:32.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate,\Nyou'll never clear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:36.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate,\NI'll break down this wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:43.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by what they said,\Nthis is a game
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:46.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in which we have to solve\Na puzzle or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:50.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… There should be\Nsome sort of hint…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's as the boy\Nwith the glasses says!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're making fun of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:00.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't indulge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're just stalling us\Nby doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They’re such a pain\Nin the neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:06.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're using a fighting style
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:08.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that restrains our power\Nand keeps it to a minimum…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,while making the best use\Nof their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:14.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to lose if\Nwe don't do this calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:17.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:18.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh?\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… That tickles…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:26.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use this room as\Nthe basis of our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This role again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:33.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is an important job\Nthat only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:36.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you put it that way,\NI guess I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be thankful to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:41.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a simple guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,\Nlet's go straight forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:52.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's…a display case?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.58,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:08.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.05,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji Abarai
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's one for Ishida as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:12.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:14.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:16.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki! Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:23.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this doesn't look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:45.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't raise…my arm…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,M-My body…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Da…mn…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:57.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:12:59.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:00.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Wake up! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Wake up! Wake up--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:06.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That…hurts, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:09.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My stuffing…is coming out…\NMy stuffing…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:10.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:11.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:19.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Let's go back to\Nthe previous room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:30.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised that you suddenly\Npassed out and collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:37.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be thankful to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:40.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did that mist have\Nhallucinogenic effects, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:53.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was close…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:06.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The floor suddenly disappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of infinite loop\Nis impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even considering the size\Nof this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even so…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:35.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the pole we tied\Nthat line of yarn to earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, put Kon down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon, don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a möbius strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:14.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They've twisted space to\Nconnect this labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:17.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why we were\Ngoing around the same place…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:19.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible for them\Nto do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:21.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only thing\NI can assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:24.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, right now,\Nwe have to solve this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:30.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing out the path\Nwe've taken…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:30.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:35.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There were traps in this\Nand this room…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to the room ahead of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there'll definitely be\Na trap in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if we move in an L shape,\Nwe won't come across any traps…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:45.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!\NThat's the secret of this labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can get past this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That would be great, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We must have missed…\Nsomething.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:16.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How many things\Ndo you have stuffed in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:20.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard those guys' voices\Nfor a while…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Use your head a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:26.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing you worked\Nas a lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:27.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of the Thirteen Court Guard Squads!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:28.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:30.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're in charge\Nof this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you did your job,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:35.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,none of this would\Nhave happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:39.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be thankful that a lieutenant\Ntook his time to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:46.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Cut it out and\Nshow yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Understand that it's pointless\Nunless we solve this puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know\Nhow to do it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:53.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:57.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Everyone's just tired\Nand annoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, I'm going to do this\Nby myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:04.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to work\Nwith you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A split among friends--!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:16.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– I wasn't this guy's friend to begin with!\N– I wasn't this guy's friend to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:28.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?\NThe space…is twisting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:32.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By this order, there's a trap\Nin that room, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Advancing in\Nan L-shaped route…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:42.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,space loops…\Nand traps that block us…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:47.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When that gate mysteriously\Nappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When Inoue and Chad\Ndisappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:53.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And ever since\Nwe've entered this building,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,this Spiritual Pressure I feel is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:57.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:58.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:00.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:02.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know the secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:04.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:06.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:10.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it really be so simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:13.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:17.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Kurosaki, lend me\Nyour Substitute Combat Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going\Nto use it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's just in case…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:28.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:32.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:43.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How did you figure out\Nthe secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:53.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We had the hint for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it out once I drew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a child's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are nine rooms placed\Nin a 3 x 3 format.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:04.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You just made them loop infinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:08.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to go three spaces\Nforward or horizontally,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we would win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:12.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So whenever we were close\Nto getting to three spaces,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you'd create trouble for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:16.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your traps were all illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:19.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was no way\Nyou could set up real traps
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to match our movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With illusions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:26.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you could lead us any way\Nyou liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We discovered the way\Nthat the traps were set
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:31.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and avoided them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that was a psychological trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:38.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our friends were kidnapped\Nand we became extra cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So we moved as a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You never expected that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:47.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we'd suddenly go\Nin separate directions and…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:51.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,by chance,\Ntake up three spaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You probably started to worry\Nwhen Kurosaki and Abarai
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:58.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,went more than nine spaces\Napart from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:02.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's when the twist\Nin space appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, finding that was\Na coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:10.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we just had to pass\Nthrough the rooms with traps…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and connect three spaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Correct…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:17.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:18.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you solve the puzzle,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:23.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the game won't end\Nuntil you catch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:36.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so,\Nyou really are mod-souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed that the small traces\Nof your Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that I felt when\NI entered the Museum,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:46.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,matched that of\NKurosaki's stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was carrying\Nthis embarrassing backpack…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:53.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I got to learn about the characteristics\Nof a mod-soul's Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:58.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji, did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:20:59.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:01.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The one who appeared\Nfrom nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,used his power to control space.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:08.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who showed us\Nthose illusionary traps?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:13.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us what you plan to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue! Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:23.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:25.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. We were just\Nsuddenly thrown out here…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:30.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:31.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to use\Nthat gate again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:36.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You won at playing\Nhide-and-seek,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so we just gave\Nyour friends back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:41.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give these back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:57.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well then…\NI'm going to start the next game!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:02.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,School is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Students should go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:05.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,School?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:08.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't go quickly,\Nyour friends will continue to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:24.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:27.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:29.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:32.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:40.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time goes by, and I get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:42.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say,\N“don’t forget that anxious feeling”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:45.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They tell me,\N“A reckless challenge is meaningless”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:47.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I say “don’t give up.”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:57.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) At times when\Nthe going gets tough, I raise my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:07.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,(Offense!) And head toward\Nthe direction of my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:17.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be afraid of\Nthat towering wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:26.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never losing sight in this life\Nwithout answers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:30.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep My Pace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:40.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count one! And move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:43.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count two! And take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:45.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Count three! And think through
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:50.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just go at my own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.05,0:23:56.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know that\Nour enemies are mod-souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:58.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we can set up a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:24:00.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't group us\Nwith a certain idiot we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:02.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:03.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You do know that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.82,0:24:06.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,she's only referring to you\Nbecause you reacted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:06.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.44,0:24:18.45,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Illustrated Guide\Nto Soul Reapers after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:21.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers…\N– Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:24.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Female Soul Reaper Association…\NIt's…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.99,0:24:26.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An official association\Nof Soul Society…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.65,0:24:30.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which was created to elevate\Nthe status of Female Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.30,0:24:32.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The matters they decide on,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.78,0:24:34.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even affect the management\Nof Central 46.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.94,0:24:36.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is a powerful underground organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.96,0:24:38.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.94,0:24:40.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.41,0:24:42.81,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-Chairwoman: Nanao Ise
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.79,0:24:42.81,DefaultLow,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our chairwoman has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.81,0:24:44.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go right ahead, Chairwoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.51,0:24:48.48,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman: Yachiru Kusajishi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.93,0:24:47.98,DefaultLow,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we play today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.48,0:24:56.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in again!